Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:31.22,paper,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(367,157)}大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:31.22,paper,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(316,181)}雨过天晴心和畅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:31.22,paper,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(319,302)}欲照山樱日影长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.72,0:09:31.22,paper,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(370,324)}运势
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太好了  小千
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十六签
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.19,0:09:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦  折木同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年看来会有好事发生呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是抽到末吉了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}末吉：一般而言，是除了凶以及大凶以外最不好的签
