Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.99,0:12:19.24,paper,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs26\frz12.66\an7\move(287,195,250,195,24,1250)}小心轻放
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我犯傻搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事  不管再怎么搞错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不认为会被关在屋子里面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  那我这就喊人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.24,0:12:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要全力喊  所以你还是捂着耳朵比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等下…  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等等啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:12:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  现在要是大声喊人过来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.90,0:12:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会发生什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…  会有人过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.95,0:13:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会帮我们拉开门闩  打开大门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在他们眼里  我们又会被看成是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些工作人员认识我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被那些工作人员们给救了的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会被误会的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.12,0:13:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  我是替父亲来这儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是换成其他时间或者地点的话倒也就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是现在在这里被发现我和折木同学你共处一室的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她所在的世界  不是我能搞懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.74,0:13:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  又该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有人过来办事  把门给打开了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:46.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是百分百会被误会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够理解我们的  也就是佳穗或者摩耶花同学了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想到了一个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:13:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.76,0:13:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用手机就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  此计甚妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有手机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.39,0:14:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀是这样啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这门看来没法拆下来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.77,0:14:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…  折木同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了折木同学你没有手机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才拜托你别大声喊人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过既然无计可施  情况就不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还是叫人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续这样下去  折木同学会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  你还是担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心被别人误会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要真是无计可施了  我会马上喊人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.33,0:14:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在那之前  我再想想有没有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折木同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既动不了门闩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也拆不下铰链
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  没探讨过的脱身方案还有四种
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么多？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.30,0:15:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一种  破门而出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.27,0:15:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二种  破墙而出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三种  挖地道逃生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四种  打穿天花板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.91,0:15:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…  可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎么旧了  这也是荒楠神社的房子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.73,0:15:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是正在巡逻中的工作人员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像捡起了一条手机链
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看得清楚？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夜视能力不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.64,0:15:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是野生动物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是要去交到社务所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社务所…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…  千反田啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.64,0:16:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这墙壁  稍微破坏一点点没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.85,0:16:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊原刚才说过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.98,0:16:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是值钱的失物  工作人员就会立即送过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而伊原在这里兼职负责失物招领
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.90,0:16:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来  我们将能表明自己身份的东西丢到外面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让工作人员交到伊原那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要让她知道我们陷入了危机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.26,0:16:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许就会来救我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.18,0:16:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于「在杂屋附近捡到的」这一点能让她起多少疑心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得看伊原她自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手帕如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩耶花同学她应该见过很多次的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  就用这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千反田  从这里把手帕扔出去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:11.78,paper,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\frz11.192\pos(248,300)}小千和折木已经到了\N来社务所等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十文字同学  新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福部同学  你有没有看到爱瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千反田同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚来  所以不清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.31,0:17:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉不能为你带路  你自己进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.79,0:17:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大客厅里点了炉子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在不太会与十文字同学相处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩耶花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿福…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在为巫女装扮而害羞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气这么冷  很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.35,0:17:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  那个电视剧怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真是杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:17:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正月第一天就笑了个痛快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:17:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  阿福  你对这个有没有印象
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得小千好像有一条这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有失主的线索是件好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.64,0:18:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等千反田同学回来了问问她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.65,0:18:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没来救我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这想法的方向性还是不错的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只有手帕看来还不够啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟不是能令人印象深刻的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  既然如此就用下一招  钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.96,0:18:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿福  快看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.02,0:18:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是奉太郎的钱包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那个笨蛋好像把这个掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.81,0:18:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙抽到的签
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:18:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉太郎抽到的是凶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.73,0:18:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然空空如也
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩耶花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我也抽一签
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里看来很灵验
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没来救我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  要是披上羽织就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.77,0:19:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽织？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.87,0:19:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是穿在和服外面的外褂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也在后悔没穿件大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里实在是有点冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  千反田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.21,0:19:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然钱包应该已经送到伊原手上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但却没能让她想到抽空来看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.35,0:19:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  该道歉的是我  让你一直迁就我的任性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是任性  是为履行自身的责任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可成不了把折木同学卷进来的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求救吧  多少有些谣言也是没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福部同学应该也已经到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.25,0:20:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  如果是里志的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折木同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千反田  你有没有绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.49,0:20:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绳子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概这么长  50厘米就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有绳子  就一定能将我们的情况传达给里志
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草鞋的带子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.59,0:20:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太短了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巾着袋上的绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.44,0:20:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巾着袋还要用到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.40,0:20:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  折木同学的鞋带呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天穿的是没有鞋带的靴子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.68,0:20:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果实在不行的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.77,0:20:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许…  可以用束腰带…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是绳子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不难解开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.99,0:20:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  算是吧  有点费事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  千反田
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对和服不太了解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:21:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把束腰带解开的话  和服不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰带…  会松掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.96,0:21:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外就没有绳子了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  为什么有绳子就能向福部同学求救呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.52,0:21:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得杂屋外面有旗子来着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.57,0:21:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折木…同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有绳子了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.85,0:21:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千反田  把巾着袋借我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个绝对是小千的巾着袋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才看到过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.72,0:22:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手帕  钱包  巾着袋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是奉太郎今天的作为吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.85,0:22:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说这个也是在杂屋外面捡到的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们两个在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.35,0:22:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还绑着一条很脏的绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.85,0:22:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绳子？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.73,0:22:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.64,0:22:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  阿福
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.43,0:22:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摩耶花  杂屋在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那边  狐仙像附近
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.97,0:22:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉太郎  千反田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.37,0:22:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就来救你们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.11,0:22:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巾着袋是口袋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.89,0:22:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把袋口和袋底绑住的话  里面的东西就被困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.78,0:22:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是「瓮中之鳖」的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.78,0:22:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\fsp2}袋中之鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.82,0:22:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓮中之鳖？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.87,0:22:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我想出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是历史上的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:22:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道姊川之战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.20,0:22:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.23,0:22:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前的著名事件  你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.56,0:23:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金崎的退口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.58,0:23:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信长进攻朝仓的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.92,0:23:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信长的妹夫  浅井叛变了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.42,0:23:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信长的妹妹  阿市将一个上下封死的豆袋送给了阵中的信长
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.29,0:23:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从而把「瓮中之鳖」的意思传达给了他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.34,0:23:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  这个故事有几分可信度就不得而知了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.06,0:23:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是有这个典故啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.72,0:23:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和里志正好今天都看了出现过这个情节的电视剧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.75,0:23:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的话应该能明白那个的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.54,0:23:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉太郎  你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.76,0:23:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.10,0:23:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都快冻死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.03,0:23:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社务所里在派发热乎乎的甜酒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.99,0:23:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就给你们开门
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.45,0:23:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.14,0:23:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开门快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.14,0:23:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14}新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.75,0:23:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.83,0:23:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开门快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.83,0:23:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs14}新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.92,0:24:02.43,EDTitle,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(320,300)}未能忘记的雏鸟（偶人）

